          "Beggars Corporation Joins ONDC Network\n\nEvent Date: 23rd May 2024\n\nBeggars Corporation, a 'for-profit' organization dedicated to uplifting the lives of beggars, has joined the revolutionary ONDC (Open Network for Digital Commerce) network. This marks a significant milestone in the organization's mission to transform beggars into successful entrepreneurs.\n\nBeggars Corporation firmly believes that the path to change lies not in hefty private donations, but in empowering individuals through training and opportunities. With their ambitious #BeggingFreeBanaras project, they aim to make the city of Banaras begging-free within three years, from April 2024 to March 2027.\n\nBy joining the ONDC network, Beggars Corporation is unlocking a world of possibilities for these newly-minted entrepreneurs. The network provides them with unprecedented market access, enabling them to showcase and sell their products to millions of potential customers across India. This level playing field is a game-changer for a section of society that has long struggled with social acceptance and limited opportunities.\n\nWe invite you to explore Beggars Corporation's e-store, where you can discover the incredible products crafted by these talented individuals. Each purchase not only supports their journey towards financial independence but also contributes to the larger goal of creating a begging-free society.\n\nJoin us in celebrating this remarkable partnership between Beggars Corporation and ONDC Network. Together, we can make a lasting impact and transform lives, one entrepreneur at a time.\n\nVisit our e-store now and be a part of this transformative journey!\n\nEnter Your Details\n\n\n\n\n\nI am a - \r\n            \r\n        Choose \r\n         Seller\r\n         Network Participant\r\n         Buyer/Customer\r\n         Others\n\n\n\nSubmit\n\nShould be Empty:\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
