          "Department for Promotion of Industries and Internal Trade (DPIIT), under the Ministry of Commerce & Industry, is organising a “ONDC Startup Mahotsav”, a mega event in collaboration with Open Network for Digital Commerce (ONDC) and Startup India. This mega event brings together startups, entrepreneurs, and innovators to foster meaningful partnerships within the ONDC ecosystem, unleashing their business potential in the realm of digital commerce.\n\nThe Mahotsav entails a diverse array of activities, including keynote addresses, panel discussions, and masterclasses by Industry experts delving into India’s unique Digital Public Infrastructure (DPI) approach to create population-scale solutions in the digital commerce sector and the myriad benefits it offers to all stakeholders of the ecosystem, particularly the startups. The event will enable startups to gain a deeper understanding of ONDC, providing them with invaluable insights and opportunities for expansion which can fuel their growth and innovation. The event will also entail real-life case studies of successful startups that have leveraged the ONDC network to  elevate their businesses to new heights. The Mahotsav presents a great opportunity for startups to embark on a journey with ONDC where collaboration, innovation, and success converge to shape the future of digital commerce.\n\nONDC Startup Mahotsav\n\nVanijya Bhawan\n\nDate: May 17, 2024\n\nRegister Now\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
