        page_content:
          "Tech Resources\n\nGet onboarded easily with tech resources\n\nTechnical resources comprise a comprehensive range of resources that are designed and tailored to ensure smooth onboarding of Network Participants on the network. These resources include a developer guide, code repositories, API specifications ion (Swagger Hub links-enabled), technical produc}t {s and white-label implementation code bases.\n\nCheck out the schedule for all ongoing community calls, which includes our regular network starter/introductory and domain-specific briefing sessions for\n\nNetwork Participants\n\nDeveloper Guide\n\nThe developer guide is designed to help and assist Network Participants on their technical journey with step-by-step instructions for seamless integration on the network. The guide gives a complete walkthrough of the API Specifications for different domains such as retail, mobility & finance, making sure Network Participants understand all the technical details from initial onboarding to advanced steps in integration on the Prod registry. It includes resources like reference materials, code snippets, illustrative examples, and frequently asked questions (FAQs) - making it easy to understand and use.\n\nWhite Label Applications\n\nFor those looking for flexible solutions, ONDC offers code frameworks for buyer and seller apps in Retail and logistics areas, known as white-label implementation. These pre-built frameworks help new Network Participants (NPs) begin their integration with the ONDC network quickly. They can adjust these frameworks to match their specific branding and needs. These implementations are regularly updated to match the latest specifications (v1.2) for the network, ensuring they're always up-to-date and in sync with the latest features.\n\nWhite Label Buyer App\n\n1. Links to access buyer app\n\nA. Staging\n\nB. Preprod\n\n2. GitHub Repo\n\n3. User Manual\n\nWhite Label Seller App\n\n1. Links to access seller app\n\nA. Staging\n\nB. Preprod\n\n2. GitHub Repo\n\n3. User Manual\n\nWhite Label Logistics Seller App\n\n1. Links to access logistics seller app\n\nA. Staging\n\nB. Preprod\n\n2. GitHub Repo\n\n3. User Manual\n\nJoin the ONDC network by submitting the Network Participants (NP) form.\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
