          "Committees and Councils\n\nUser Council\n\nNetwork Expansion Council\n\nCapacity Building Council\n\nUser Council\n\nNetwork Expansion Council\n\nCapacity Building Council\n\nAbout User Council\n\nONDC has constituted the User Council to create a forum for participatory governance as part of its commitment to transparency and inclusivity. The User Council is intended to be a forum for stakeholders in the ONDC Network to contribute towards the governance and development of the Network.\n\nUser Council Members\n\nTo ensure representation to a diverse set of network participants, the User Council consists of members belonging to  various stakeholders of the ONDC Network such as representatives of Network Participants, varying by the role played on the Network (Buyer App, Seller App, Logistics Service Providers), across different categories and size of the organisation. The User Council also includes external stakeholders who can bring in useful expertise to the forum. The following list are the Members of the User Council, which have been assigned by the ONDC Board of Directors\n\nMr. Lalit Singh, General Manager, Shopping Business, PhonePe Pvt. Ltd. Pincode\n\nMr. Saahil Goel, CEO & Founder, BigFoot Retail Pvt. Ltd., Shiprocket\n\nMr. Vijay Shekhar Sharma, CEO, One97 Communications Pvt. Ltd., PayTM\n\nMr. Vimal Kumar, CEO & Founder, Juspay Technologies Private Limited\n\nNew members to be added soon\n\nUser Council meetings\n\nS. No. Meeting Date Summary of proceedings 1 1st User Council meeting 14th December 2022 2 2nd User Council meeting 30th January 2023 3 3rd User Council meeting 28th March 2023 4 4th User Council meeting 18th May 2023 5 5th User Council meeting 21st November 2023\n\nNetwork Expansion Council\n\nCapacity Building Council\n\nONDC Participant Portal\n\nBegin and efficiently manage your journey on ONDC Network\n\nUnderstand and select your role(s)\n\nTrack, manage and troubleshoot your integration\n\nDiscover and collaborate with others\n\nStay informed on network developments and announcements\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
