          "India will open up through the ONDC Network. Access to all kinds of sellers and all kinds of products & services across India is now available on this Open Network.\n\nFind out how\n\nIn the current shopping landscape, in an app or website you're confined to only what's available there. To access other options, you have to explore additional apps or websites. ONDC Network brings to you a ground-breaking change, or what we call the future of shopping!\n\nUnbundled. Transparent. Open.\n\nThe Open Network connects all platforms through technology making all buyers and sellers transact with each other regardless of which app they are on. Now, you can choose from an entire selection of sellers and as well as products available through any app on the network - all within a single, unified app or website.\n\nMore\n\nWhat you must know about shopping via the ONDC Network?\n\nYou have the freedom to pick from any of multiple shopping applications, known as buyer apps. Through any one of these apps, you access the entire spectrum of products and services available on the network. They differ in experience so you may choose whichever suits your preferences the best.\n\nThe network boasts over 5.52+ Lakh sellers/service providers encompassing 12 product categories growing by thousands every week. However, it's important to note that at this early stage of the network, not all apps accommodate every product and location. As the network expansion continues, this limitation will soon become a thing of the past and you'll be able to utilise any of your preferred apps to explore and buy any category of product or service.\n\nTo get started choose your category of interest, and we will show you which buyer apps can help you shop from sellers of that particular category on the ONDC Network.\n\nRethink how you shop\n\n1. Choose the category you want to shop\n\n1. Choose the category you want to shop\n\n2. Pick a buyer app from the list provided\n\n2. Pick a buyer app from the list provided\n\n3. Browse and place your order\n\n3. Browse and place your order\n\n4. Get order confirmation\n\n4. Get order confirmation\n\nAfter an order is placed successfully on the network, you start getting order updates. You may receive these notifications from multiple companies as there are a number of multiple partners involved in fulfilling your order in this digital revolution that we call an ‘open network’.\n\nExplore a comprehensive range of products and services\n\nProducts\n\nTravel\n\nServices\n\nComing Soon\n\nFood & Beverages\n\nGrocery\n\nFashion\n\nElectronics\r\n                                    & Appliances\n\nHome & Kitchen\n\nBeauty\r\n                                    & Personal care\n\nHealth & Wellness\n\nGift Card\n\nToys & Games\n\nComing Soon\n\nAuto\n\nCab\n\nMetro\n\nWater Taxi\n\nComing Soon\n\nTrain\n\nComing Soon\n\nBus\n\nComing Soon\n\nB2B\n\nComing Soon\n\nChoose a Buyer Application\n\nShop Now\n\nShop Now\n\nShop Now\n\nNote:\n\nAs the network matures, many more categories and domains will be added by the network and also be enabled by ONDC Protocol compliant buyer application.\n\nRedirecting to paytm.com\n\nIt may takes up to 10 seconds\n\nRedirect\n\nCancel\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
