          "ONDC Looks To Onboard News Media Platforms On The Network\n\n\n\nBy \xa0 ONDC\n\nApr 25, 2024\n\nUpdated: Apr 25, 2024\n\n1 min read\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nHome\n\nBlog\n\nNews\n\nONDC Looks To Onboard News Media Platforms On The Network\n\nPublication - Inc42 Media\n\nEdition - Online\n\nLooking to bolster its category play, the Open Network for Digital Commerce (ONDC) is reportedly looking to onboard news media platforms on the state-backed network.\n\nAs part of this move, the digital arm of Hindi media giant Dainik Jagran is in advanced stages of integration with ONDC, Moneycontrol reported.\n\nPlease click on the link below:\n\nONDC Looks To Onboard News Media Platforms On The NetworkLooking to bolster its category play, the ONDC is reportedly looking to onboard news media platforms on the state-backed network.Inc42 MediaBhupendra Paintola\n\nNews\n\nKeep reading\n\na year ago · 1 min read\n\nONDC is making e-commerce space democratised for all players\n\nNews\n\na year ago · 2 min read\n\nTransactions in ONDC seeing growth across the board\n\nNews\n\na year ago · 1 min read\n\nTomato Price Rise: NCCF To Sell Subsidised Tomatoes On ONDC In Delhi\n\nNews\n\nONDC Participant Portal\n\nBegin and efficiently manage your journey on ONDC Network\n\nUnderstand and select your role(s)\n\nTrack, manage and troubleshoot your integration\n\nDiscover and collaborate with others\n\nStay informed on network developments and announcements\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
