          "Government push to help ONDC get shopfront on ecommerce sites\n\n\n\nBy \xa0 ONDC\n\nApr 29, 2024\n\nUpdated: Apr 29, 2024\n\n1 min read\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nHome\n\nBlog\n\nNews\n\nGovernment push to help ONDC get shopfront on ecommerce sites\n\nPublication - Economic Times\n\nEdition - Online\n\nThe Centre has asked Amazon and Flipkart to set up Open Network for Digital Commerce (ONDC) storefronts on their home pages to help the government-backed network scale up operations and assist with deliveries, said executives aware of the development. The aim is to boost operations and order efficiencies as well as iron out glitches and delays on ONDC, the said.\n\nPlease click on the link below:\n\nGovernment push to help ONDC get shopfront on ecommerce sitesThe Centre has asked Amazon and Flipkart to set up Open Network for Digital Commerce (ONDC) storefronts on their home pages to help the government-backed network scale up operations and assist with deliveries, said executives aware of the development. The aim is to boost operations and order efficie…Economic TimesRatna Bhushan and Suraksha P\n\nNews\n\nKeep reading\n\na year ago · 1 min read\n\nONDC is making e-commerce space democratised for all players\n\nNews\n\na year ago · 2 min read\n\nTransactions in ONDC seeing growth across the board\n\nNews\n\na year ago · 1 min read\n\nTomato Price Rise: NCCF To Sell Subsidised Tomatoes On ONDC In Delhi\n\nNews\n\nONDC Participant Portal\n\nBegin and efficiently manage your journey on ONDC Network\n\nUnderstand and select your role(s)\n\nTrack, manage and troubleshoot your integration\n\nDiscover and collaborate with others\n\nStay informed on network developments and announcements\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
