          "VP-Infromation Security\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nHome\n\nCareer\n\nVP-Infromation Security\n\nJob Description\n\nThe primary responsibility of this position is to set the strategic course and develop a comprehensive program for cyber resilience. This entails ensuring robust data security and privacy measures for the business, implementing effective cybersecurity practices and governance frameworks, and establishing a scalable operational framework that mitigates risks in today's complex business environment. Additionally, the role involves overseeing all assurance activities related to the availability, integrity, and confidentiality of customer, business partner, employee, and business information. This is done in alignment with ONDC policies governing information, digital assets, data, and other relevant areas. Furthermore, the position involves collaborating with executive management to define acceptable risk thresholds for the organization.\n\nRoles and Responsibilities\n\nEstablishing state-of-an-art security framework for the network to interoperate in unbundled framework\n\nContinuously evaluate the ONDC protocol and specifications and suggest/advise improvements to protect the network from potential threat vectors\n\nMonitor, analyse and audit security apparatus of our participants interfacing with ONDC network\n\nKeep the network participants abreast with contemporary and latest development in cybersecurity arena\n\nProtect ONDC digital assets, such as Registry, Gateway, Network observability infrastructure etc against any potential threat\n\nPreferred Qualifications\n\nPossess 12 to 18 years of experience post-qualification.\n\nAccumulate 8 to 10 years of experience specifically in information security operation, architecture, and service delivery management within eCommerce, technology, or related industries.\n\nApply Now\n\nJobs\n\nProduct Manager\n\nBusiness Analyst\n\nVP-Logistics\n\nApply For\n\nSame as Permanent Address\n\nExperience *\n\nProfile Photo *\n\nResume *\n\nONDC Participant Portal\n\nBegin and efficiently manage your journey on ONDC Network\n\nUnderstand and select your role(s)\n\nTrack, manage and troubleshoot your integration\n\nDiscover and collaborate with others\n\nStay informed on network developments and announcements\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
