          "The power of ONDC\n\n\n\nBy \xa0 ONDC\n\nOct 21, 2023\n\nUpdated: Oct 21, 2023\n\n1 min read\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nHome\n\nBlog\n\nNews\n\nThe power of ONDC\n\nPublication - India Retailing\n\nEdition - Online\n\nFirst up, ONDC is not a platform like Amazon but a network of enterprises coming together to enable digital commerce. It is a two-sided network with buyer apps on one side and seller apps on the other side. Buyer apps bring traffic into the network and seller apps bring supply. Companies like Paytm, Phonepe, Meesho, Craftsvilla, Ideamasters, and Bluestar are part of this network playing the role of either a buyer app or a seller app. This network approach has bigger benefits compared to the platform approach of e-commerce companies today. Any seller or retailer can participate in digital commerce without bias on ONDC.\n\nPlease click on the link below:\n\nThe power of ONDCWith the right building blocks, ONDC will enable seamless commerce for 50 crore customers and 5 crore SMEs in this countryIndia RetailingManoj Gupta\n\nNews\n\nKeep reading\n\na year ago · 1 min read\n\nONDC is making e-commerce space democratised for all players\n\nNews\n\na year ago · 2 min read\n\nTransactions in ONDC seeing growth across the board\n\nNews\n\na year ago · 1 min read\n\nTomato Price Rise: NCCF To Sell Subsidised Tomatoes On ONDC In Delhi\n\nNews\n\nONDC Participant Portal\n\nBegin and efficiently manage your journey on ONDC Network\n\nUnderstand and select your role(s)\n\nTrack, manage and troubleshoot your integration\n\nDiscover and collaborate with others\n\nStay informed on network developments and announcements\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
