          "Is ONDC the future for Indian E-commerce Sellers?\n\n\n\nBy \xa0 ONDC\n\nJul 21, 2023\n\nUpdated: Jul 21, 2023\n\n1 min read\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nHome\n\nBlog\n\nNews\n\nIs ONDC the future for Indian E-commerce Sellers?\n\nPublication - Livemint\n\nEdition - Online\n\nIn the ever-expanding digital landscape, where the rules of business are constantly evolving and consumer expectations are reaching new heights, ONDC, the government-backed initiative, has emerged as a true game-changer. \xa0The Open Network for Digital Commerce (ONDC) is restructuring the way businesses operate and transforming the dynamics of consumer interactions. \xa0With its aim to establish an open and transparent digital network for e-commerce transactions, ONDC brings a wealth of advantages to the table, reshaping the entire digital commerce ecosystem.\n\nPlease click on the link below:\n\nIs ONDC the future for Indian E-commerce Sellers?With its aim to establish an open and transparent digital network for e-commerce transactions, ONDC brings a wealth of advantages to the table, reshaping the entire digital commerce ecosystemmintHT Brand Studio\n\nNews\n\nKeep reading\n\na year ago · 1 min read\n\nONDC Academy : Your guide to e-commerce enabled by the ONDC Network\n\nONDC Academy\n\nONDC\n\nDigital\n\n2 years ago · 1 min read\n\nONDC is now Beta testing in Meerut!\n\nBusiness\n\nONDC\n\n2 years ago · 2 min read\n\nONDC Incentive Program for Bengaluru Plus:  Inviting all interested participants starting 16th December.\n\nBusiness\n\nONDC\n\nONDC Participant Portal\n\nBegin and efficiently manage your journey on ONDC Network\n\nUnderstand and select your role(s)\n\nTrack, manage and troubleshoot your integration\n\nDiscover and collaborate with others\n\nStay informed on network developments and announcements\n\nNo results for your search, please try with something else.",
